    "name": "Live Project #2API Testing -|| RESTfull Booker",
    "description": "E2E Test Suite for RESTful Booker API\n\n## Overview\nThis comprehensive test suite validates the full functionality of the RESTful Booker API, ensuring robust and reliable API interactions across various scenarios.\n\n## Test Objectives\n- Validate complete API workflow from authentication to resource management\n- Ensure data integrity and correct response handling\n- Verify error handling and edge cases\n\n## Test Coverage\n### Authentication\n- Token generation\n- Authentication validation\n- Access control checks\n\n### Booking Management\n- Create new bookings\n- Retrieve booking details\n- Update existing bookings\n- Delete bookings\n- Partial updates\n\n## Validation Criteria\n- HTTP Status Code Verification\n- Response Body Structure Validation\n- Data Type and Format Checks\n- Error Scenario Handling\n\n## Test Workflow\n1. Authenticate and obtain access token\n2. Create a new booking\n3. Retrieve and validate booking details\n4. Perform booking updates (full and partial)\n5. Delete booking\n6. Validate error scenarios and edge cases\n\n## Best Practices\n- Consistent test data generation\n- Independent test case design\n- Minimal test dependencies\n- Comprehensive error handling\n\n## Performance Considerations\n- Response time tracking\n- Minimal API call overhead\n- Efficient test execution",
